I was so excited when I heard that some of the former Recollections girls were opening up their own shop in Peoria!
This shop does not disappoint.
Crop Girls offers a great selection of paper, stamps, and embellishments too.
The variety that they have in their shop is quite amazing.
Everything is well organized so it is easy to find.
The owners are super helpful and kind.
You can tell they really love their shop and are happy to help if you have any questions.
Prices are great too!

