So it is unusual for a man to leave a review for a scrapbooking store but I accompany my wife to this store a lot.
The staff is great!
Very friendly and helpful.
I like the fact that they let me pile my stuff on a corner of their counter instead of carrying a load around (my wife buys tons of things here).
Their selection is pretty cool too.
They even have some stuff that I found myself liking and I actually bought a few things and started making my own dream journal.
If you are a scrapbooker, this is a great place to get supplies at.
I hear that the name will be changing to Scraps Of Love soon but the owner will still be there and my wife (and me too) will be going here for a long time to come!
-Mari's Husband Keith

